- cs.OS (Operating Systems): The paper deals with scheduling in real-time systems, which is a core topic in operating systems. 
- cs.EM (Embedded Systems): The paper specifically mentions designing embedded systems, and the techniques proposed are applicable to such systems. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper focuses on distributed real-time systems, which falls under the purview of distributed computing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with analyzing the behavior of systems, which is a core topic in systems and control. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper mentions the implementation of the proposed techniques in software tools, which falls under the purview of programming languages.
